    },
    {
      "id": "a08b17e2-effd-48a5-b4b4-de53015856ad",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Não tinha medo, dava o João no santo Cristo, era o que todos diziam quando ele escreveu",
      "message_type": "ooc",
      "timestamp_start": 6.86,
      "timestamp_end": 9.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:20:54.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:20:57.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "bee8bdf2-691c-4e3b-808a-97ed84f8a6fd",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Fechou o padrastro do marado da fazenda, só tá sentindo seu sangue, o ódio que já surpreendeu",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 9.86,
      "timestamp_end": 12.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:20:57.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:00.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "83d54a36-f526-4351-9c94-0b213902a073",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Quando o fião só pensava em ser bandida, ainda mais do que um tiro do soldado pra morrer",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 12.86,
      "timestamp_end": 15.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:00.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:03.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "7fb30dde-3652-4640-8099-9b15fe4e62cf",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "No terror da cercaninha onde morava na escola, até o professor com ele ia prender",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 15.86,
      "timestamp_end": 18.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:03.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:06.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "da98ba5e-2ae3-463a-ae5e-8f9a9c4e9599",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ia pra igreja só pra roubar no tigre, a peça que ele insolucava na caixinha do altar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 18.86,
      "timestamp_end": 20.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:06.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:08.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "e9459ceb-1725-496d-95dc-92aedd57930c",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Sentia mesmo que era mesmo diferente, sentia que o alião era o seu lugar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 20.86,
      "timestamp_end": 23.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:08.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:11.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "c5171dbc-85a9-4d0c-8878-6da331554509",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ele queria sair para ver o mar, as coisas que ele via na televisão",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 23.86,
      "timestamp_end": 26.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:11.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:14.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "8ce59cb2-0da7-4865-bec8-1910891cd28a",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Juntou dinheiro para poder viajar, escolhei a prova, escolhei a solidão",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 26.86,
      "timestamp_end": 29.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:14.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:17.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "1ce06fac-3773-4723-9df6-0a5e71f37b8a",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Comi a todas as meninas da cidade, distribui um par de médicos, você era a pessoa",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 29.86,
      "timestamp_end": 32.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:17.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:20.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "7d74d432-2501-4ee8-afee-17e7c9b01b32",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "O que eles quisam foi mandar pro reformatório, onde aumentou seu adjeto de dança terror",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 32.86,
      "timestamp_end": 35.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:20.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:23.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "d028c400-4b98-4228-8dfa-96a6834b9bad",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Não entendia como a vida funcionava de se liminhar, só por causa dessa classe morrida",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 35.86,
      "timestamp_end": 38.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:23.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:26.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "367d1b56-ead2-409c-b18e-f6205b725344",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E foi alcançado de tentar, já a escola se comprou uma passagem, foi ditada ao salvador",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 38.86,
      "timestamp_end": 41.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:26.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:29.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "35c78b84-4e16-47ec-814b-0816300fcff5",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E lá chegando foi tomado um padrastrinho, botando boiadinho e foi falar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 41.86,
      "timestamp_end": 44.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:29.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:32.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "d0790225-2b20-4b90-9094-1cc591f4c664",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Não podia ter, eu tinha uma passagem, ia perder a viagem, mas o povo me salvava",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 44.86,
      "timestamp_end": 47.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:32.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:35.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "dfcf649e-302e-4e35-9c92-03964c798cb3",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Dizia a ele, estou indo pra Brasília, nesse país lutar melhor não há",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 47.86,
      "timestamp_end": 50.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:35.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:38.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "2645656d-1ab7-475f-afe7-964a3cdbfbcc",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E se usar no visitar, minha filha, eu fico aqui e você vai no meu lugar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 50.86,
      "timestamp_end": 53.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:38.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:41.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "bb6777a8-8166-4e7c-8aad-3b666903aac8",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Me chamou uma cinquânsula, depois o ônibus entrou no plano central",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 53.86,
      "timestamp_end": 56.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:41.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:44.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "e52666b4-f524-4db5-9c4f-449bd4f877f2",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ele ficou esticado na cidade, saindo da holofiada, viu a tosse de natal",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 56.86,
      "timestamp_end": 59.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:44.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:47.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "6d2f0584-257a-42d2-b5b3-3ed46d4c6f8d",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ele começou a trabalhar, com a madeira que dizia, eu venha pra aquele que tem que fazer a tinta",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 59.86,
      "timestamp_end": 62.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:47.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:50.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "fed9c3c4-c819-4d0c-93be-66917b336e3d",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "A cinquenta, soma da cidade da tosse, eu te viro de natal, trafalhador",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 62.86,
      "timestamp_end": 65.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:50.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:53.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "b8db1fe4-4164-4073-90d4-070017f47a5f",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E conhecia a unidade que ele deixou antes, até onde eu fui passar, com o seu viso a cor",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 65.86,
      "timestamp_end": 68.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:53.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:56.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "497e9b63-1957-4835-acd8-b7a2e65bf20a",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Pelo quanto ele vivia na bolígada, ele nunca soube da cidade lá",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 68.86,
      "timestamp_end": 71.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:56.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:21:59.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "adc6acc9-870a-40af-8d5e-59547447cba0",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Seu nome era Pablo, ele dizia, que nem o negócio ele ia conversar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 71.86,
      "timestamp_end": 74.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:21:59.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:02.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "93f16506-95c3-40ea-87b9-b7c7cd9197e5",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Só se que essa terra foi estrapalhada, mas o tio não tava a felicidade de estar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 74.86,
      "timestamp_end": 76.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:02.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:04.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "6757b2b5-24b0-47ef-bc0a-75aee0f1f8d9",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E eu via cedir o associaio, que sempre tinha que ser o índice de agitar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 76.86,
      "timestamp_end": 79.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:04.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:07.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "984f7555-1326-4825-b9e7-0b81aad78080",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Mas ele não queria mais conversas desse tipo, como Paulo, ele queria sequirar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 79.86,
      "timestamp_end": 82.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:07.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:10.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "d9edc139-ed21-4fd5-9e1b-a4af1670a099",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ele alugou mais uma vez o plano santo, sem ter que ficar a botança pra começar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 82.86,
      "timestamp_end": 85.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:10.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:13.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "b6f7f32b-1ec7-422b-9bc3-482864d3bc32",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "O que foi, boy?",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 86.86,
      "timestamp_end": 87.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:14.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:15.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "dece90eb-72be-4de5-95c5-3fa08edb1973",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Enxurrou seu viso e foi virar a boca de todos, da que deve ser dele",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 87.86,
      "timestamp_end": 89.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:15.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:17.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "e6c04f54-2b7b-46db-affe-c690ad683fef",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Preferindo se enfrentar a máscara, a que a pareda dizia, pra se libertar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 89.86,
      "timestamp_end": 92.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:17.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:20.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "28c2192f-d83f-4dc5-91f7-969b43f57662",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "A que, de repente, o meu mamãe, imponência do sozinho da cidade, veio só a roubar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 92.86,
      "timestamp_end": 95.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:20.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:23.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "400ca7e1-76b9-478d-a17b-8dd7221adff9",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "De qualquer um, ele não soube do que é feio pela maneira bem-estruida",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 95.86,
      "timestamp_end": 98.86,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:23.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:26.422000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "98d4116f-529d-4540-b44c-4190b97f118d",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E o legismo do que sobrou, um de todos os artigos, ele se arredendeu",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 98.86,
      "timestamp_end": 110.75,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:26.422000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:38.312000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "b30f493d-d8e2-4e9d-990e-7038e2b3c91d",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Maria Luz era uma menina linda, com a sua linda era, e o seu viso foi teu",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 110.75,
      "timestamp_end": 113.75,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:22:38.312000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:22:41.312000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "bbfb357b-e828-4cf5-9c56-601de4e54f54",
